{"tid":540392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[中國的...]【火燒高鐵】安徽列車行駛中起火冒濃煙 1400客冒雪驚逃","createTime":"2018-01-25T12:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T12:48:21.000Z","uid":60665,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a48289d9e34c28adce5cff80a6de0d58c9dd799f","tid":540392,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:27:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180125/57752214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57752214&d=R%2BWC1h81c5tTGwnIebQPrNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=94f7f955\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180125%2F57752214&h=b964c41b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180125/57752214</a><br />\n今日一列從山東青島開往浙江杭州的高鐵，行駛至安徽省滁州市期間，第二節車廂着火，火勢相當猛烈，列車在暴雪中緊急在當地的定遠縣停車，1,400名乘客慌張逃生，紛紛爬上月台。<br />\n涉事的是G281次列車，有列車上的乘客指出今日約11時半，列車行駛時車廂便着火冒煙，但列車的人員沒有馬上停車，而是繼續開行至定遠站才疏散乘客。現場拍到的片段顯示，高鐵冒出濃濃黑煙，更冒出火光。<br />\n鐵道部門指出，這列高鐵有16個車廂，共載有1,400人，事故是2號車廂的電器設備發生故障冒煙，事故未造成傷亡。<br />\n新浪微博  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516860632_752d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516860632_752d.jpg&h=035518cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516858954_7acb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516858954_7acb.jpg&h=3ccaf176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516861225_7b50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516861225_7b50.jpg&h=29f806d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180125/large/1516861227_58b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180125%2Flarge%2F1516861227_58b3.jpg&h=27423784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/oBnvzp2B9xA/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FoBnvzp2B9xA%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=3aedc015&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba81cc01e5a777170ac86846b2651361691ef1c2","tid":540392,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:31:35.000Z","msg":"舊既唔燒新既點黎啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726ddbb72a2c573f04d60662ffb95a04deaf911c","tid":540392,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:34:23.000Z","msg":"又冇電油又冇電池可以燒到咁大火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c50acd62ba55a37626b96198c60c104f8e3599","tid":540392,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:36:31.000Z","msg":"著火叫動車呀"},{"pid":"dad9569567c2fc713264e11bea80e2e6ca1b1b51","tid":540392,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:42:38.000Z","msg":"燒通頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你車廂0防火 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c1deb6e0c9344880cae790ff3dcbc0339449d1","tid":540392,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T12:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}